## Description {#details}

This class represents DWARF information for source file and it&#39;s address map.

May be used asynchroniously for reading.

Definition at line 25 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/dwarflinker/dwarffile-h">DWARFFile.h</a>.
